typedef int(* DLList_data_cmp_func)(void *data1, void *data2)

type of function to pass to the mergesort to compare the data

Parameters:
data1 the first data pointer to be compared
data2 the second data pointer to be compared
Returns:
less than 0 if data1 is less than data2 0 if data1 is equal to data2 greater than 0 if data1 is greater than data2
note if data is a char pointer strcmp() can be passed
